# Curated local mirror of assertion-focused examples.

GET __BASE_URL__/status/200

> EXPECTED_RESPONSE_STATUS 200

###

GET __BASE_URL__/status/404

EXPECTED_RESPONSE_STATUS 404

###

GET __BASE_URL__/headers
Accept: application/json
X-Test-Header: test-value

EXPECTED_RESPONSE_STATUS 200
EXPECTED_RESPONSE_HEADERS content-type: application/json

###

GET __BASE_URL__/json

EXPECTED_RESPONSE_STATUS 200
EXPECTED_RESPONSE_BODY "slideshow"

###

GET __BASE_URL__/uuid

EXPECTED_RESPONSE_STATUS 200
EXPECTED_RESPONSE_BODY "uuid"
